TITLE: Decoupling Types for Reusability in ArkType with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create separate, reusable type definitions in ArkType. The 'Device' type is defined independently and then used within the 'User' type.
SOURCE: https://github.com/arktypeio/arktype/blob/main/ark/docs/content/docs/intro/your-first-type.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
