TITLE: Basic JSON Parsing with Pipe in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use ArkType's pipe method to transform a string into an object by parsing JSON. Shows both successful parsing and error handling when invalid input is provided.
SOURCE: https://github.com/arktypeio/arktype/blob/main/ark/docs/content/docs/intro/morphs-and-more.mdx#2025-04-11_snippet_0

